"                                2                         3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned above, a reflection occurs when a beam emerges from the same "
"point it was sent in. This can happen in several ways:"
msgstr ""
"Kot je navedeno zgoraj, do odboja pride, ko žarek izhaja iz iste točke, "
"kamor je bil poslan. To se lahko zgodi na več načinov:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"- - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - O - - -         - - O - O - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"R * * * * - - - -         - - - * - - - -          O - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - O - - -         - - - * - - - -        R - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -       R * * * * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -          - - - - - - - -"
msgstr ""
"- - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - O - - -         - - O - O - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"R * * * * - - - -         - - - * - - - -          O - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - O - - -         - - - * - - - -        R - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -       R * * * * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -          - - - - - - - -"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the first example, the beam is deflected downwards by the upper ball, "
"then left by the lower ball, and finally retraces its path to its point of "
"origin. The second example is similar. The third example is a bit anomalous "
"but can be rationalized by realizing the beam never gets a chance to get "
"into the box. Alternatively, the beam can be thought of as being deflected "
"downwards and immediately emerging from the box."
msgstr ""
"V prvem primeru se žarek odbije navzdol z zgornjo kroglo, nato levo s "
"spodnjo kroglo in končno sledi svoji poti do svoje izhodiščne točke. Drugi "
"primer je podoben. Tretji primer je nekoliko nenavaden, vendar ga je mogoče "
"racionalizirati z ugotovitvijo, da žarek nikoli ne dobi priložnosti priti v "
"škatlo. Lahko pa si zamislimo, da je žarek odklonjen navzdol in takoj "
"izstopi iz škatle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "A hit occurs when a beam runs straight into a ball:"
msgstr "Zadetek se zgodi, ko je žarek usmerjen naravnost v kroglico:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"- - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - O - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -        H * * * * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -       H * * * * O - - -          - - - * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -          - - - O - - - -\n"
"H * * * O - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -"
msgstr ""
"- - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - O - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -        H * * * * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -       H * * * * O - - -          - - - * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -          - - - O - - - -\n"
"H * * * O - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be sure to compare the second example of a hit with the first example of a "
"reflection."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite primerjati drugega primera zadetka s prvim primerom odboja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Board Description"
msgstr "Opis igralne plošče"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kblackbox; Game Board</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kblackbox; Igralna plošča</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kblackbox; Game Board</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kblackbox; Igralna plošča</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following types of field are found on the game board:"
msgstr "Na igralni plošči so naslednje vrste polj:"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The big black box in the middle"
msgstr "Velika črna škatla na sredini"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you must mark the positions you think a ball is in."
msgstr "Tukaj morate označiti položaje, na katerih mislite, da je kroglica."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lasers around the box"
msgstr "Laserji okoli škatle"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lasers are shooting beams of light when switched on. Then, they "
"disappear and are replaced by an information about the interactions of the "
"laser beam with the balls in the black box."
msgstr ""
"Laserji ob vklopu oddajajo svetlobne žarke. Nato izginejo in jih nadomesti "
"informacija o interakcijah laserskega žarka s kroglicami v črni škatli."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balls"
msgstr "Kroglice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>There must be one there!</quote> you think. These mark where you "
"suspect a ball is placed in the black box."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Tam mora biti ena!</quote> mislite. Te oznake označujejo mesto, kjer "
"sumite, da je v črni škatli postavljena kroglica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the end of the game, the right and wrong positions of the balls are also "
"marked with <quote>balls</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu igre so pravilni in napačni položaji kroglic označeni tudi s "
"<quote>kroglicami</quote>."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Markers for \"free position\""
msgstr "Oznake za \"prost položaj\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use them to mark some positions where you are sure there is no ball."
msgstr ""
"Z njimi lahko označite nekatere položaje, kjer ste prepričani, da kroglice "
"ni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game (and abandons the current, if any.)"
msgstr "Začne novo igro (in opusti trenutno, če obstaja.)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pause or continue the current game."
msgstr "Zaustavite ali nadaljujte trenutno igro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that the interaction results are hidden in a paused game."
msgstr "Upoštevajte, da so rezultati interakcije v zaustavljeni igri skriti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži najboljše rezultate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the high score tables."
msgstr "Pokaži tabele z najboljšimi rezultati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start Tutorial</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Začni vadnico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start the tutorial of the game. This is a user friendly way to learn the "
"game rules."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite vadnico igre. To je uporabniku prijazen način za učenje pravil igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Sandbox Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova igra v peskovniku</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode, the solution is displayed at the start of the game. This is "
"useful to understand the game principles."
msgstr ""
"V tem načinu se rešitev prikaže na začetku igre. To je koristno za "
"razumevanje načel igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "This closes the window and quits &kblackbox;."
msgstr "To zapre okno in zapre &kblackbox;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Solve</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use it to give up a game. It shows you the solution: the right positions of "
"the balls."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ga, da opustite igro. Pokaže vam rešitev: pravi položaji kroglic."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Done!</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Končano!</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you placed all the balls, choose <guilabel>Done!</guilabel> to "
"terminate the current game, to compute the final score and to display the "
"real positions of the balls."
msgstr ""
"Ko postavite vse kroglice, izberite <guilabel>Končano!</guilabel>, da "
"končate trenutno igro, izračunate končni rezultat in prikažete dejanske "
"položaje kroglic."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the game difficulty. Harder games have more balls and bigger black "
"box than easier games. You can also play with a custom difficulty level that "
"you can set up in the setting dialog of &kblackbox;."
msgstr ""
"Izberite težavnost igre. Težje igre imajo več kroglic in večjo črno škatlo "
"kot lažje igre. Igrate lahko tudi s težavnostno stopnjo po meri, ki jo lahko "
"nastavite v nastavitvenem pogovornem oknu &kblackbox;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Games with 4 balls or less can always be solved with certainty! That is not "
"the case for games with 5 balls or more."
msgstr ""
"Igre s 4 kroglicami ali manj je vedno mogoče rešiti z gotovostjo! To ne "
"velja za igre s 5 kroglicami ali več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kblackbox; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kblackbox; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje te igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. You can use the directional keys to control the cursor, &Enter; to "
"place and remove balls, and &Space; to place <quote>empty</quote> marks."
msgstr ""
"Da. Za upravljanje kazalca lahko uporabite smerne tipke, &Enter; za "
"postavitev in odstranjevanje kroglic ter &Space; da postavite <quote>prazne</"
"quote> oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kblackbox; has no save feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kblackbox; trenutno nima funkcije shranjevanja."

